title: Jessica Simpson: Blonde. Billionaire. Boss | Resurrection | 4
description:
For the first time ever, Jessica has everything she’s ever wanted — a loving husband, beautiful kids and a thriving business. But now that she’s on top of the world, there’s nothing to distract her from the hurt she’s been carrying since she was six years old…
